## 5. Results and Discussion

### 5.1 Training Setup

All training was conducted on Windows 11 with AirSim configured for 84x84 depth-only rendering using the FlyWithMe viewport mode. The depth-only camera configuration reduces pixel throughput by approximately 58x compared to the default 1080p RGB rendering, significantly increasing the achievable training frames per second (FPS) while retaining all information relevant to obstacle avoidance.

