The PPO baseline was trained using the exploration reward function without domain randomisation to establish performance baselines before adding complexity.

[PLACEHOLDER: Table 4 -- PPO baseline results over 20 evaluation episodes: collision_rate (fraction), average_speed (m/s), path_smoothness (m/s^3), survival_time (s), mean episode reward. Report mean +/- std across 3 random seeds.]

